@page "/"

<PageTitle>AeroPartsTracker — Home</PageTitle>

<link href="css/home.css" rel="stylesheet" />

<div class="home-root">

    <div class="home-hero">
        <div class="home-hero-badge">Programming Languages · Spring 2025</div>
        <h1 class="home-hero-title">
            Aerospace Parts<br />
            <span class="home-hero-accent">Tracker</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="home-hero-sub">
            A student engineering suite built for the Programming Languages course at Bethel College.
            Three interconnected modules apply real computational mathematics to aerospace manufacturing problems.
        </p>
        <a href="parts-manufacturing" class="home-cta">
            Open Engineering Suite
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12" />
                <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19" />
            </svg>
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="home-modules">

        <div class="home-module-card">
            <div class="home-module-icon geo">
                <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <polygon points="12 2 22 20 2 20" />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="home-module-tag">Module 1</div>
            <h3>Part Geometry Validation</h3>
            <p>
                Input three 3-D surface coordinates. The app computes the plane equation,
                unit normal vector, and perpendicular distance from the origin using
                cross products and dot products — verifying that a machined bracket face
                meets its angular specification.
            </p>
            <div class="home-module-tech">Linear Algebra · Cross Product · Dot Product</div>
        </div>

        <div class="home-module-card">
            <div class="home-module-icon tol">
                <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12" />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="home-module-tag">Module 2</div>
            <h3>Tolerance Stack-Up Analysis</h3>
            <p>
                Enter a part ID, nominal dimension, standard deviation, and sample size.
                The app returns the 95% confidence interval, probability of conformance,
                and Cp / Cpk process capability indices — flagging machining drift before
                non-conforming parts are produced.
            </p>
            <div class="home-module-tech">Statistics · Normal Distribution · MathNet.Numerics</div>
        </div>

        <div class="home-module-card">
            <div class="home-module-icon bom">
                <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <circle cx="9" cy="21" r="1" />
                    <circle cx="20" cy="21" r="1" />
                    <path d="M1 1h4l2.68 13.39a2 2 0 0 0 2 1.61h9.72a2 2 0 0 0 2-1.61L23 6H6" />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="home-module-tag">Module 3</div>
            <h3>BOM Optimizer</h3>
            <p>
                Select quantities for three assembly types, each with fixed screw demands.
                A brute-force integer optimizer finds the minimum-cost combination of
                small, medium, and large fastener packs — reducing procurement waste
                across production lines.
            </p>
            <div class="home-module-tech">Integer Optimization · Brute-Force Search</div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="home-features">
        <div class="home-feature-item">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" /></svg>
            Real-time validation & loading indicators
        </div>
        <div class="home-feature-item">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" /></svg>
            ApexCharts — normal distribution curve & pack bar chart
        </div>
        <div class="home-feature-item">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" /></svg>
            History log — last 5 calculations per module
        </div>
        <div class="home-feature-item">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" /></svg>
            mm / in unit conversion toggle
        </div>
        <div class="home-feature-item">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" /></svg>
            PDF export via print stylesheet
        </div>
    </div>

</div>
